29
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,640
the more it makes me feel

30
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,120
that I'm not cut out for it.

31
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,440
Don't say that.

32
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,500
You started acting since childhood.

33
