A man at five may be a fool at fifteen.

34
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,400
Doesn't your mother always say that?

35
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:58,960
Does your mother really

36
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,360
hate me so much?

37
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,360
She calls me a jobless

38
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,600
every time she comes here.

39
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,040
She knows that I'm allergic to that sauce,

40
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,200
but she still brings it here every time.

41
