109
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,720
when you two are alone.

110
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,160
But it's not a big deal

111
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:14,840
and we don't

112
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,440
