193
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,360
Very long ago, when we were in high school.

194
00:08:57,720 --> 00:09:00,040
So I didn't let you go into my room.

195
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,080
That was early-maturing!

196
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,740
You're being late-maturing.

197
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:06,200
What if I got married

198
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,360
when you were

199
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,680
in Singapore?

200
